def_cn: （与名词连用构成形容词）表示“…领导的”，“…管理的”，“…控制的”
def_en: -led combines with nouns to form adjectives which indicate that something is organized, directed, or controlled by a particular person or group.

def_cn: （与名词连用构成形容词）表示“…起主导作用（或影响）的”
def_en: -led combines with nouns to form adjectives which indicate that something is mainly caused or influenced by a particular factor.
